accessibility.text: Her parents felt happy that she called them. Her family was in the middle of a feast on the other side of the earth, where she's not able to join. Thinking about how far she is from the family that she grew up with, she feels so sad that she couldn't control her emotions.

Her parents spotted that she acted in a weird way and ask her if she's okay. Should May tell them that she's spending her Chinese New Year's night in the hospital? But her parents are going to be so depressed and worried if they know.
